Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Trafalgar Law and \Nhave come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped in the Birdcage \Nalong with the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting \Nthe Don Quixote Family fiercely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Law are heading \Nto the Royal Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This jerk! What is he up to?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an all-or-nothing gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm determined to bet my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father-sama must be\Nsomewhere on this battlefield, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody made it here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go straight to the fourth level this way!\NLet's go, Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it helps Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rooster-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...worth risking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Tearful Reunion!\NRebecca and Kyros!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry or\NSoldier will kick Mingo's ass first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use fighting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at the fourth level!\NShake it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:39.31,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE PLATEAU - LOCATION OF THE ROYAL PALACE - LEVEL 4\NTHE SUNFLOWER FIELD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're here to kill Doffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You recklessly challenged me\Nwith that blunt-edged sword
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and disgraced yourself pathetically!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know you have no chance against Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you came to challenge me again\Nbelieving in some miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To avenge your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I couldn't protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! If you wanna challenge me,\NI accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen to me, Rebecca!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll kick Doflamingo's ass for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shame on you, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?! Why are you running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a gladiator!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you came to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I'm no match for Diamante.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I have to do now is\Nhand this key over to Lucy and the others!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the Colosseum, I managed to put on\Nsome good shows using you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you can't fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've served your purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... put an end to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You prefer a gun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...got killed by a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't let you take away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...another member of my family\Nfrom me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This man was a legend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the strongest gladiator\Nin the history of the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I couldn't protect your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna protect you to the end,\Nwith my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teach you how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother said I shouldn't hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you how to not get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain and wind will rust my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long my body's gonna last!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father-sama...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a toy with no future,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nall I could do was teach you how to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're a gentle person\Nlike your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it ends today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't have to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Kyros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means, today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll settle my score with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's the end of all of {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! We both made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we caught up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!\NThe fourth level - where Mingo is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, you two...\NMy hands are full with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take care of Doflamingo for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll leave that guy up to you, Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go, Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're happy to see your dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to \Ntake down Doflamingo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Luffy!\NThe man who'll become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting me, Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What annoying bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get to the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tremendous idiot! Traitorous brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a useful ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is but it also eats up my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, having those Sea Prism Stone cuffs on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and getting carried by you to this \Npoint wasn't so bad after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to save my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I operated on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He purposely used lead bullets...\NThat jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No need to worry.\N--I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NLet's go and kick Mingo's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo isn't someone that you can \Nbeat just by force of will alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How can I cool down\Nafter getting this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, if you don't,\Nyou can't defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping here won't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law and Straw Hat have shown up\Nin the yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...nearby the pool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Roger that.\N--Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 years... For 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent such a long time,\Nincreasing their number little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tens of thousands of toy slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...brought it all to naught in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, Kanjuro?! We have no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just touch them with this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your existences...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to naught!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A vengeful Sugar closes in on Luffy and Law.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Won't let her turn him into a toy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWith this passionate thought in his mind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.28,0:23:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Usopp takes aim at Sugar in the distance,\Nbeyond even his line of sight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.80,0:23:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suddenly, everybody's fate depends on\NUsopp's skill!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Shot One Kill! The Man \NWho Will Save Dressrosa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:51.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
